{
  "stem": "9590.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I said to her, Malka, you know what you-- please help me and do something for me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "So she said, you don't have to ask me, you know that I would do my best.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And for a moment, I reminded myself the story about Jana Finkiel and what she told me when she left Babi Yar and emerged in that outhouse.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I asked them if I can go out to relieve myself.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "He said, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I went out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And over there, where the outhouse was, I was ready to do what Jana did.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And then I looked around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And near it, was another door.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And was a little room with a bed where the farmhand slept.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "It was his quarters.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So rather than to jump in that filth, I went into that, opened the door, and went in there, and tried to push myself under the bed.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was very thin.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was able to push myself under the bed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And with straw, covered myself all around and lied flat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Outside, I heard-- I couldn't see, because I was inside-- but I heard outside a big commotion-- screaming and shooting.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that went on for a long time, for a long time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was lying motionless, not knowing what's going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was sure that my mother and my brother went away, because that's what my mother told me, that she is going away to look for another place.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the evening, that farmhand came and lied down on the bed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was under that bed, lying flat, afraid to breathe even.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then I heard, again, a commotion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The police came and were looking for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I heard them say in Ukrainian, where is that [NON-ENGLISH] girl?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She disappeared under our hands.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
